spec_data.Name: yum-plugin-rpm-warm-cache
spec_data.Description:
This plugin reads the rpmdb files into the system cache before accessing the
rpmdb directly. In some cases this should speed up access to rpmdb information
spec_data.Signature: RSA/SHA256, Fri 28 Jul 2017 09:03:01 PM EDT, Key ID f55e7430f5282ee4
spec_data.Summary: Yum plugin to access the rpmdb files early to warm up access to the db
